translation[9]{c,v,t}:
  15,91,"Abenza\ti’Kur’ân\tibe\tzizahlulo\tngezahlulo\t(bakholwe kwinxalenye yayo bangakholwa kwenye)"
  15,92,"Inene (Ndifunga) ngeNkosi yakho (Muhammad), Siza kubabiza bonke beze embuzweni (ngezenzo zabo)"
  15,93,Ngako konke oko bakwenzayo
  15,94,"Wena ke vakalisa ngaphandle [ungawufihli (uMyalezo ka- Allâh)] lowo uyalelwe ngawo. Uzikhwebule kubakhonzi bezithixo"
  15,95,Inene Thina Siya kukwenza wanele uwedwa ngokuchasene nabagculeli
  15,96,"Abayamanisa omnye uthixo kuAllâh, kodwa baza kwazi kungekudala"
  15,97,"Inene, Thina Siyazi okokuba intliziyo yakho icinezelekile ngenxa yoko bakuthethayo"
  15,98,"Ke wena zukisa ngendumiso iNkosi yakho, ube ngomnye wabo baqubudayo kuYo"
  15,99,Uyinqule iNkosi yakho kananjalo kude kufike isiqinisekiso esiyinyani (ukufa)
  16,1,"Onyankopͻn ahyεdeε no aba, enti εmma mo mpere ho. Kronkron Hene ne no; Ɔkorͻn kyεn deε wͻde bata Ne ho no."
  16,2,"Ɔnam N’ahyԑdeԑ so ma Soro abͻfoͻ no de Honhom (Adiyisεm) no sane ba Ne nkoa no mu nea Ɔpε so sε: “Mommͻ (adasamma) kͻkͻ sε: “Awurade foforͻ biara nni hͻ ka Me ho, enti monsuro Me”."
  16,3,"Ɔde nokorε no na abͻ soro ne asaase, Ɔyε Okokuroko korͻn paa kyεn deε wͻde bata Ne ho no."
  16,4,"Ɔbͻͻ nipa firi ahobaeε mu, na hwε sε ͻno ne otiafoɔ pefee."
  16,5,"Ɛna Wabͻ nyεmmoa nso ama mo; wͻn ho no monya (ntaadeε a) εma mo ͻhyew, san (nya) mfasoͻ pii firi wͻn ho; na wͻn mu bi nso mowe (wͻn nnam)."
  16,6,"Monya wͻn ho anigyeε nso wͻ berε a mode wͻn reba fie anwummerε ne εberε a mode wͻn rekͻ adidie anͻpa."
